cl-smt-solver
=============

Pure Common Lisp SMT Solver

This software was originally developed as part of the CLPIC project.
It has been extracted as a standalone library for general use.

The implementation includes:
- DPLL SAT solver with conflict-driven clause learning
- Theory solvers for Boolean, Integer, and Bitvector domains
- High-level verification API

